beIN SPORTS 3.desc: This will be the fifth meeting between Athletic Club and Sporting CP, with the most recent coming in the 2011-12 UEFA Europa League semi-finals; Marcelo Bielsa’s Athletic won 4-3 on aggregate to reach the final, which remains one of only two European finals they’ve reached in their history. The home team has won in all four meetings between Athletic Club and Sporting CP, with Athletic’s two victories on home soil coming in November 1985  and April 2012.

beIN SPORTS 3.original_title: Borussia Dortmund vs Internazionale Milano - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.title: Borussia Dortmund vs Internazionale Milano - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.desc: Borussia Dortmund and Internazionale have faced each other on six previous occasions in Europe, with the most frequent result being an Inter victory. The last meeting between Borussia Dortmund and Internazionale was a 3-2 victory for the German side in November 2019 – a game that Inter led 2-0 in at half time. This remains the only time that Dortmund have trailed by 2+ goals at half time of a European Cup/UEFA Champions League game and gone on to win, as well as the only time Inter have led by 2+ goals at the break and lost in those competitions.

beIN SPORTS 5.original_title: Al Ittihad Club (KSA) vs Shabab Al Ahli (UAE) - AFC Champions League Elite 2025/2026 - West MD2

beIN SPORTS 5.desc: This will be the first meeting between Al-Ittihad and Shabab Al Ahli in AFC Champions League Elite history; teams from Saudi Arabia have won seven of their last eight games in the competition against teams from UAE, however, the one loss in this run was Al-Ittihad’s 1-2 loss to Al Wahda in their opening matchday of the 2025-26 season. Al-Ittihad have lost each of their last three AFC Champions League Elite games, their joint-longest run of such games in the competition, including a 1-2 loss to Al Wahda on Matchday 1; Al-Ittihad have never lost each of their first two games of an AFC Champions League Elite campaign and only twice have they failed to win any of their first two games.

beIN SPORTS 8.original_title: Crvena zvezda vs Celta de Vigo - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.title: Crvena zvezda vs Celta de Vigo - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.desc: Crvena zvezda and Celta de Vigo met in the 2000-01 UEFA Cup second round – the Serbians won 1-0 in the first leg but lost 3-0 in the second leg and were eliminated. This is the second time in the last two seasons Crvena zvezda will face a Spanish side – they were beaten 5-2 at home by Barcelona in last season’s UEFA Champions League.

beIN SPORTS 8.original_title: Eintracht Frankfurt vs Tottenham Hotspur - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.title: Eintracht Frankfurt vs Tottenham Hotspur - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.desc: Tottenham have faced Eintracht Frankfurt on six occasions in major European competition, with Feyenoord  being the only opponent they’ve faced more often. They have lost just one of the previous six, while they’re unbeaten in the last four – all of which have been since 2022-23. Tottenham have lost just 17% of their meetings with Eintracht Frankfurt  – of opponents they have faced 5+ times in major European competition, only versus Sparta Prague  do they have a lower loss percentage.

beIN SPORTS 8.title: FCSB vs Fenerbahçe - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.desc: FCSB and Fenerbahçe have faced in the UEFA Europa League before, meeting twice in the 2009-10 group stage – the Turkish side won both matches. Fenerbahçe are unbeaten in their last four away matches in Romania in all European competition  since losing 1-0 to Petrolul Ploiesti in October 1963 in the Cup Winners’ Cup.

beIN SPORTS 8.original_title: Pafos vs Slavia Praha - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.title: Pafos vs Slavia Praha - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.desc: Pafos versus Slavia Prague will be the first ever European Cup/UEFA Champions League match played between teams from Cyprus and Czechia. This will be the first time Pafos have faced an opponent from Czechia in European competition, while Slavia Prague have only faced a Cypriot side in one previous campaign, being eliminated by APOEL Nicosia in qualifying for the 2017-18 UEFA Champions League.

beIN SPORTS 8.title: Genk vs Malmö FF - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.desc: Genk and Malmö met in the 2018-19 UEFA Europa League group stage – the Belgian side won 2-0 at home, while there was 2-2 draw in Sweden. beIN SPORTS 8.original_title: Sturm Graz vs Brann - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.title: Sturm Graz vs Brann - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 8.desc: Sturm Graz and Brann have never met before in European competition – the Austrian side have won both of their previous home games against Norwegian teams, beating FK Haugesund and Bodø/Glimt in August 2019 and August 2025 respectively in European competition’s qualifiers. Brann were knocked out of UEFA Champions League qualifying by Austrian side FC RB Salzburg earlier this season 5-2 on aggregate, their only previous games against a team from Austria.
